added.title: Sheep Bears
added.description: The Bears get jobs as sheep herders on an idyllic farm.

added.title: Ice Bear's Pet
added.description: Ice Bear attempts to keep a giant owl-monster secretly as a pet.

added.title: Memories of Bobby
added.description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

added.title: The Curse
added.description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

added.title: The Last Kid in the Creek
added.description: A terrible curse leaves Craig as the only kid in the creek.

added.title: Squirrels Squirrels Squirrels
added.description: Courtney's attempt to make Chef a better teacher fails when a squirrel gets his hands on her mind-control device.

added.title: Say Hello to my Little Friends
added.description: After telling the kids he will not miss them over the long weekend Chef locks himself into the school and finds out he was very, very wrong.

added.title: WaterHose-Five
added.description: The hottest day of the year and a broke air conditioner leads to a water battle of epic proportions to determine who controls the garden hose.

added.title: Cody the Barbarian
added.description: Cody is set to inherit a video game empire from his long lost uncle, but only if he and his friends have what it takes to conquer a fantastical live action video game.

added.title: TP2: Judgement Bidet
added.description: When the city experiences a toilet paper shortage Beth and Harold investigate and discover it's their old rival Sewer Mike who is the mastermind behind it all.

added.title: Villainy In Monte Macabre
added.description: In a crossover episode with the show Villainous, V&V team up with Dr. Flug and Demencia to try to find a squid monster who is disguised as a human in Monte Macabre.

added.title: The Cupcake Man
added.description: When Victor's bad behavior gets out of control, Chata sends him to the one man in town who can set him straight, The Cupcake Man.

added.title: Charlene Mania
added.description: When Vic attempts to have the perfect day off, the town's sudden obsession for Charlene gets in his way.

added.title: Old Man Teo
added.description: When Vic and Val are tasked to volunteer at an Old Folks' Home, Val becomes buddies with the oldest, crankiest person in Monte Macabre and helps him reclaim his youthful power.

added.title: Poacher Patrol
added.description: When Don bestows Val the responsibility of patrolling the lake, Val takes it too far and stops who he believes to be a poacher -- with disastrous consequences.

added.title: #WorkingStiff
added.description: After Babs hooks Karen up with a job at the Burrito Bucket the two heroes encounter a new villain, the scourge of the fast-food underworld, the Condiment King!

added.title: #MultipliciZee
added.description: Zee magically duplicates herself so she can shirk work and watch TV. Things get out of hand when her copies start to make copies of themselves!

added.title: #TheMinus
added.description: Diana receives her first ever A minus and becomes convinced that she needs to work harder, however, in order to do so, she resorts to rather drastic measures.

added.title: #Powerless
added.description: Supergirl loses her powers and, with the help of BumbleBee, must rely on her street smarts to save Garth from vengeful Toyman.

added.title: #AcceptNoSubstitute
added.description: Feeling smothered, Babs urges her retired dad, Commissioner Gordon, to get a hobby, but her advice backfires when the Commissioner becomes a substitute teacher at her school!

added.title: Idiosyncratic Induction
added.description: On Elliott's first day at the Hive, he meets the most unusual characters on his adventure so far.

added.title: Memory Mayhem
added.description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

added.title: The Speedway Five-Billion
added.description: Unagami's soldiers, the Red Visors, finally discover the secret location of Scott's garage and attack the ninja, who manage to escape with the help of Racer Seven, and enter the spectacular Speedway Five Billion.

added.title: Stop, Drop and Side Scroll
added.description: Our ninja barely have time to mourn the loss of their fallen ninja friends before being thrust into the madness of Terra Domina where Lloyd will have to face an old adversary from his past.

added.title: Ninjago Confidential
added.description: Back in Ninjago City, Zane and Pixal hit the mean streets to track down Milton Dyer, only to discover that things are not what they seem.

added.title: The Prodigal Father
added.description: Zane, kidnapped by the Mechanic, faces Unagami. Master Wu fights to free Zane, while Pixal questions Milton Dyer for information on how to shut down Prime Empire.

added.title: The Temple of Madness
added.description: Jay must stand alone against Unagami in the end-game, yet Unagami has a bigger battle in facing the truth about his own identity.

added.title: Everything's Fine
added.description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

added.title: I Am My Monster
added.description: Everything is not fine.

added.title: Magnus P.I.
added.description: There's a been a string of thefts and each one has involved a Bakugan. The AAAnimus security force have decided the only brawler who could be responsible is: Magnus. The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

added.title: The Mysterious Revenger/Wynton vs. Lia
added.description: The Mysterious Revenger: It's the quarter finals of the Bakugan Battle League, the top eight brawlers are set to face off! In this round, Dan will face off against the Bakugan rocker - Revenger! These two brawlers give it their all in this icy cold clash!/Wynton Vs. Lia: The quarter finals continue, and it's the first Awesome Brawler vs. Awesome Brawler matches of the Bakugan Battle League tournament. In this round, it's Wynton vs. Lia and Shun vs. Lightning.

added.title: Bobo Chan
added.description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

added.title: Small
added.description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

added.title: Legend of Torbaclaun
added.description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

added.title: Meet Tanya Keys
added.description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

added.title: Weapon of Choice
added.description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

added.title: Recuerdos de Bobby
added.description: Cuando un importante miembro de la comunidad del Arroyo se marcha, el trío lamenta su pérdida recordando los buenos tiempos.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Carrera Cinco Billones por Hora
added.description: Los soldados de Unagami, los Visores Rojos, finalmente descubren la ubicación secreta del garaje de Scott y atacan a los Ninjas.

added.title: Detenerse, Caer y Girar
added.description: Los Ninjas no han ni llorado la pérdida de sus amigos  caídos cuando ya deben entrar a la locura de Tierra Domina.

added.title: Ninjago Confidencial
added.description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Zane y Pixal salen a las calles para encontrar a Milton Dyer, y descubren que las cosas no son lo que parecen…

added.title: El Padre Prodigo
added.description: Zane, secuestrado por el Mecánico mientras Pixal interroga a Milton Dyer para obtener información sobre cómo cerrar el Primer Imperio.

added.title: El Templo de la Locura
added.description: Jay debe enfrentarse solo a Unagami en el juego final, pero Unagami tiene una batalla más grande al enfrentarse a la verdad sobre su propia identidad.

added.title: La Maldicion
added.description: Craig, Kelsey y JP entran en conflicto con unas brujas adolescentes deshonestas, ique les lanzan una maldición! iQué adolescentes malvadas!
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Bobo Chan
added.description: Colosal adopta a un monstruo abandonado, pero es mejor dejar algunas cosas en estado salvaje.

added.title: Pequeno
added.description: El legendario, gigantesco y crítico padre de Mao Mao visita a su hijo en su nuevo trabajo como sheriff.

added.title: Todo Esta Bien
added.description: Steven insiste en que todo está bien.

added.title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun
added.description: Cuando los Corazoncitos creen que el mítico Torbaclaun ha llegado al Valle Puro Corazón, Mao Mao intenta demostrarles que no es real.

added.title: Soy Mi Monstruo
added.description: No todo está bien.

added.title: Conozcan a Tanya Keys
added.description: Cuando Tanya Keys, la cazadora de recompensas, llega a la ciudad para atrapar a Colosal, Mao Mao y Adorabat son los encargados de salvar a su amigo... aunque se haya metido en asuntos ilegales.

added.title: Arma de Eleccion
added.description: Preocupado de que su espada sea un premio consuelo con pretensiones, Mao Mao decide salir a demostrar el valor de su arma.
